content: By far my favorite deck. I've had a set of these cards forever now since my early 20s at least so since they came out and I love that I have the digital option for online clients now and definitely appreciate the work that went into.the app. It does need a update but other than that message I get that it's out of date I highly recommend as it's amazing.
I use this deck daily to learn it, I appreciate the beauty and bluntness of the messages. Having the ap makes looking up meanings much easier. Happy with my purchase.

I already own the physical deck and love using it, so this review will be only about the app. The app has no way of adding new spreads to it, and that's a major negative for me. Learning and creating new spreads is part of my tarot work and this app lacks that facility. The free form option is too inflexible to substitute for that. Spreads are almost as important as the cards themselves, so I may stick with the Uni Tarot app for now.

This has all of the features you could want from a tarot app (including a built-in card tracker and journal) and makes it easy to learn the cards without having to carry a physical deck or book around with you. I love it and use it every day. As someone who is using this deck to learn tarot for the first time, I'm a big fan of this app.
Beautiful cards and always spot on.
Vibrant colors. Beautiful version of this beautiful deck. I would like Empress to be spelled correctly though.
My favorite tarot deck ever. And this app works perfectly. Highly recommend to all.
My favorite tarot deck, by far. Love everything about them
It's unlike other decks, it's fun, and dark. I like it for my go to deck when I'm in a different mood or mindset.
I personally find this deck a bit disturbing but my best friend loves it. It's not a deck for the faint of heart but if you connect with it, you'll form a strong bond.
Very Accurate which is scary!! I love this deck!!.

The most amazing tarot app I've ever used! My readings are super accurate. And the ART! Omg, the art is to die for; so beautiful that I find myself just getting lost in their lush colors and characters, and it helps me understand each card better. Love it so much I bought the physical deck! I highly recommend Deviant Moon to everyone interested in tarot, from novice to expert; you won't be disappointed!!!
I love this deck.
Beautiful artwork.
I love this deck. I have the physical deck as well. I love having the deck in my phone to use whenever I need. One of the most accurate decks I have ever used.
Accurate reads, superb art. Rather dark deck Not, for the faint of heart. Fast favorite.
This deck is amazing! The app us very user friendly and great for beginners!
Really helped me to learn the deck!

The artwork we fans have come to love are available on our phones. What's not to love? Absolutely worth the $4, or however much it is now. Do Tarot readings directly from your phone, choose cloths, keep notes, & have daily cards as a widget. There are free Tarot card apps out there, but those don't have this artwork.
A little tricky to get used to, but very insightful when you do.
Love this deck
I love this app! I most use my Deviant Moon deck but this app is great for when I'm out and about. This is my favorite tarot deck!
awesome app! I can play with tarot cards anytime I like! Plus this deck is the best.....
love this app, imaginative, useful, beautiful and well designed

I bought this app after I bought the actual tarot deck. I have no regrets. I use it to learn cards as it's much easier to look at the card meanings on the app rather than in the tiny book that came with the tarot deck. The app runs very smoothly and I can even input manual spreads I do outside of the app. I really like the card of the day widget that comes with it. I say totally worth the one time payment. Beautiful artwork.
love it

This is a phenomenal deck of extraordinary dark beauty and eccentricity. Even if you don't read tarot cards, the deck is worthy of your art aesthetic. A Groundbreaking tarot deck in every way!!!! Patrick Valenza is genius in the truest sense of the word and a very nice individual!

100% HANDS DOWN THE BEST and ONLY CARDS U SHOULD USE. THE ART WORK OF THE ARTIST IS TRULY DIVINE AND WILL SPEAK TO U. ALL THE OTHER DECKS ARE RETARDED . AND LAME ARTWORK. EW if u use those. i feel sorry for u. they arent youthful or unique. lame af
I have an early version of these cards and an so exited they are in app form as well. With all the amazing selections The Fool's Dog has done a great service for the Tarot community. Thank you!
accurate...hauntingly beautiful cards
beautiful quality in the cards very easy to use and understand especially for beginners
I love the Deviant moon tarot. As a reader of Tarot, Patrick Valenza's creepy cute characters are wonderful in this deck, so much so, I bought the physical deck. Blessed be.
wonderful deck. beautiful art. fantastic readings
Very nice app for learning this deck. Nice images you can zoom in on. Please make an app for Patrick Vallenza's other decks!
Beautifully made, incredible graphics.
The best format for a tarot app i have come across.
I love this deck and this app is fantastic
i used these myself love them . adore
The art is striking and bizarre and i love it. The art reflects traditional imagry and meanings with unusual, thought provoking art. Well done!
Great for daily tarot.
Beautiful cards, easy to discern
Good

Love everything about this app and deck. Easy to use and love the fact you 
can make your own spread. Very satisfied!!
SUPER...super COOL+FANTASTIC -AMAZING & BEAUTIFUL too

Wonderful app! Great for those times when I'm out and about and don't have 
my deck at hand. Easy to use, images are brilliant, With lots of lovely 
features. Highly recommend!
Fun and beautiful cards!
Love it! Beautiful art

It's with a heavy ❤️ I write this. I love this deck and removed other apps 
to have room to purchase this. The card reproductions are terrific. The app 
runs like a typical Fools Dog app so the app itself is amazing, but the 
meanings for the cards are nothing more than a skimpy LWB explanation. I 
hope someday it gets updated to something more substantial. I have 8 other 
Fools Dog tarot apps and as far as the written text goes, this is the 
worst. I love Deviant Moon and Fools Dog but am dissatisfied with this combo

Beautiful art work. The readings are good but somewhat esoteric for a beginner like me. I struggle to relate the reading to the question I asked. Hopefully I will get better at that. The range of spread options is fab. I love that you can even select just one card.
I love this deck its my favorite one the art work is amazing
This deck is fantastically well thought out and executed. If you're thinking the style is not for you, give it a chance.
I LOVE the Deviant Moon tarot and I LOVE having the app on my phone for when I don't have my cards. Highly recommend! ♡♡♡
Perfect companion app for my physical deck! I love the journal and card of the day features.
Has amazing features and is very well put together...i use it every morning...

I own this deck and it's actually one of my favorites. I've had it for years and tend to use it when I need to ask myself the hard questions and work through my own issues. This is just more convenient than carrying around a deck in my fast paced lifestyle.
Super beautiful detail of my favorite book! Love the custom spread option! 6/5 stars!
Love this app. Have the deck but wanted to use it on my phone. Great.
Favourite beautiful deck. In a handy portable app.
In love with Deviant Moon

Surprisingly accurate, I own a physical deck as well and both answer same question with exact cards and placement. I enjoy the artwork as well as it's easy to read and helpful instructions and meanings
Great...
Excellent app, just like the deck. I do prefer actually touching the cards, but this works great when you need some clarity in a pinch!
Beautiful and accurate app. So glad to have it.
The pictures are beautiful in an eerie way, and oddly compelling. There is a lot of depth to this tarot deck.
I've own a deck of The Deviant Moon Tarot and I love them.
I love this deck!
Gorgeous, fantastical, helpful to this beginner.
Amazing tarot deck that's even more amazing on the go. This is a deck that will really speak to you.
Thank you!!!
Pretty awesome!!!
My favorite deck is now an app! This is very useful and informative. So glad I downloaded this.

I fell in love with this deck when I bought it almost 3 years ago. Now I can take it anywhere in app form & stay under the radar if needed! It's always at my fingertips. Amazing graphics, user-friendly, & thorough. My favorite feature is the journal. Well done Patrick, et al.
Love this deck. And now? The app. Yay!
One of the best decks in recent years!
Amazing images, VERY accurate - thank you for adding this! Not for everyone, but glorious.
I have been waiting for this deck for some time. THANK YOU for adding it!
